"* Conversions from the built-in Integer to the arbitrary-precision stdlib number types.
"* (BigInteger / BigDecimal themselves are native — src/runtime/big_integer.rs,
"* src/runtime/big_decimal.rs — registered before this loads.)
Integer <-- {
    "* This Integer as an exact arbitrary-precision BigInteger.
    "*
    "* ```
    "* 2.asBigInteger.pow:100    "* -> 1267650600228229401496703205376
    "* ```
    asBigInteger -> { BigInteger.of:self }
}
